{"id": 62476, "date": "2025-11-27T04:00:26", "date_gmt": "2025-11-27T12:00:26", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=62476"}, "modified": "2026-07-01T11:51:44", "modified_gmt": "2026-07-01T18:51:44", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-november-27-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/11/27/kingdom-of-days-november-27-2/", "title": {"rendered": "November 27"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1958:\u00a0</strong>Nine-year-old Bruce Springsteen celebrates Thanksgiving with his family. (Can you spot him?)</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"23258\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1958-11-27/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1958-11-27.jpg?fit=550%2C416&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"550,416\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1958-11-27\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1958-11-27.jpg?fit=550%2C416&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-23258 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1958-11-27.jpg?resize=550%2C416&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"416\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1958-11-27.jpg?w=550&amp;ssl=1 550w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1958-11-27.jpg?resize=300%2C227&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1970:\u00a0</strong>Steel Mill opens for two Cactus and Black Sabbath shows at Asbury Park&#8217;s Sunshine In.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uZV-rKsHjEg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Iakqd7kgV2A?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"46508\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/asbury_park_press_fri__nov_27__1970_/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Asbury_Park_Press_Fri__Nov_27__1970_-scaled.jpg?fit=2560%2C1553&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2560,1553\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&q