sl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1068,562\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1971-11-27\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-11-27.png?fit=758%2C399&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-22861 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-11-27.png?resize=758%2C399&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"399\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-11-27.png?w=1068&amp;ssl=1 1068w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-11-27.png?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-11-27.png?resize=1024%2C539&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1971-11-27.png?resize=768%2C404&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>The holidays are approaching! When Bruce and the E Street Band bring the Darkness Tour to the Mecca Arena in Milwaukee, they dust off &#8220;Santa Claus is Comin&#8217; to Town&#8221; for the season.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/yOft2r-2IsY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"14320\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/47491500642_fa4e3e24cd_o/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/47491500642_fa4e3e24cd_o.jpg?fit=828%2C648&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"828,648\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"47491500642_fa4e3e24cd_o\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/47491500642_fa4e3e24cd_o.jpg?fit=758%2C593&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14320 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/47491500642_fa4e3e24cd_o.jpg?resize=758%2C593&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"593\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/47491500642_fa4e3e24cd_o.jpg?w=828&amp;ssl=1 828w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/47491500642_fa4e3e24cd_o.jpg?resize=300%2C235&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/47491500642_fa4e3e24cd_o.jpg?resize=768%2C601&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1980:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays a Thanksgiving Day concert at Madison Square Garden in New York City, and he tells a special Thanksgiving-themed story during &#8220;Growin&#8217; Up&#8221; to mark the occasion.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Lsz2RPMWoY8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"14321\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/40492583443_560665e215_o/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/40492583443_560665e215_o.jpg?fit=1200%2C595&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1200,595\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"40492583443_560665e215_o\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/40492583443_560665e215_o.jpg?fit=758%2C376&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14321 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/40492583443_560665e215_o.jpg?resize=758%2C376&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/40492583443_560665e215_o.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-conte