tps://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1980-11-27a.png?resize=1536%2C411&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1980-11-27a.png?resize=2048%2C548&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"22863\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1980-11-27b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1980-11-27b.png?fit=2080%2C611&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2080,611\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1980-11-27b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1980-11-27b.png?fit=758%2C223&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-22863 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1980-11-27b.png?resize=758%2C223&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"223\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1980-11-27b.png?w=2080&amp;ssl=1 2080w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1980-11-27b.png?resize=300%2C88&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1980-11-27b.png?resize=1024%2C301&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1980-11-27b.png?resize=768%2C226&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1980-11-27b.png?resize=1536%2C451&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1980-11-27b.png?resize=2048%2C602&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1982:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Jimmy and The Mustangs on stage at Club Lingerie in Hollywood for &#8220;Twist and Shout.&#8221;</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"6525\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1982-1127/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1982-1127.jpg?fit=770%2C1068&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"770,1068\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1982-1127\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1982-1127.jpg?fit=738%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-6525 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1982-1127.jpg?resize=758%2C1051&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1051\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1982-1127.jpg?w=770&amp;ssl=1 770w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1982-1127.jpg?resize=216%2C300&amp;ssl=1 216w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1982-1127.jpg?resize=768%2C1065&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/1982-1127.jpg?resize=738%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 738w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1995: </strong>The\u00a0<em>Tonight Show with Jay Leno </em>features a guest appearance by Bruce, who performs &#8220;The Ghost of Tom Joad.&#8221; The performance will eventually be released on\u00a0<em>Video Anthology.</em></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/1ujE0eql_sY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Bruce&#8217;s appearance was taped during the day. That night, he plays his second of two shows at the Wiltern Theater in Los Angeles, where Bruce debuts a brand new song, &#8220;It&#8217;s the Little Things That Count.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2clbTQ5N7-8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong>One day prior to the beginning of the last leg of\u00a0<em>Springsteen on Broadway</em>, the promotional push for Bruce&#8217;s Netflix special begins with the publication of a feature article in\u00a0<em>Esquire.</em></p>\n<p><strong>2022:\u00a0</strong>HBO premieres <em>The Howard Stern Interview: Bruce Springsteen</em>, filmed live in SiriusXM Studio in October.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zQ2KrFoFqao?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/B7cd03N4jN8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uZi79ulSp4E?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Steel Mill opens for Black Sabbath, Bruce makes a Tonight Show appearance, and it&#8217;s the world premiere of &#8220;It&#8217;s the Little Things That Count.&#8221; More highlights inside.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 70275, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky